net.dv8tion.jda.core.managers

Class GuildManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dv8tion.jda.core.managers.GuildManager

  • public class GuildManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Facade for a GuildManagerUpdatable instance.
    Simplifies managing flow for convenience.

    This decoration allows to modify a single field by automatically building an update RestAction
